'''Martha Veitch''' was an author who wrote the short story ''[[A Hunter's Fate: Greedo's Tale]]'', in which she fleshed out [[Greedo/Legends|Greedo's]] backstory prior to his demise in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']]. She was also married to late [[Star Wars: Tales of the Jedi (comic series)|''Tales of the Jedi'']] author [[Tom Veitch]]. Martha died on [[September 11]], [[2022]].<ref name="Death" />

